title: Purchase list (28/10/2021) for MC DAO
body:
This proposal is made today and will end at 3:30PM EST in order to allow some of the most upvoted proposals on the discord proposals channel to have snapshot votes on, and one of these in the list will be passed through to be purchased around 3:30PM EST (might be later than 3:30PM EST) before the gorilla launch (which is at 7PM EST). All of these purchases listed will be bought at bare minimum floor prices at the time of buying, (e.g. when any of these in the list is selected, we will do a floor sweep of that project with no tolerance above floor.) 

The list is as follows (the prices are at time of writing): 

1) 20-30 MAYC (Floor) = 80-120 ETH
2) 1 CryptoPunk (Floor, Fish Head) = 96 ETH
3) 1 Genesis CyberKongz (Floor) = 125 ETH
4) 1 Fidenza (Floor) = 135 ETH
5) 10 AB Squiggles (Floor) = 100 ETH
